  <h3>How to Give Online:</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>
      <strong>Go to</strong>
      <a href="http://giving.stanford.edu">giving.stanford.edu</a> and click on
      the main menu "Make a Gift Now" ("Direct Your Gift" pops open)</li>
    <li>
      <strong>Direct your gift:</strong>
      At the first drop down selection choose 'other', select the type of gift
      (one time, pledge, recurring), select payment type (credit card, wire
      transfer, or security transfer), and click continue.
      <p>*You will need to Log In or Register if you haven't already</p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Designate your Gift:</strong>
      In the 'Further Designation' drop-down menus select 'Other Designation
      (specify below)'. In the Special Instructions/Other Designation Text Box
      write <strong>Stanford Men's Lacrosse</strong>.
    </li>
    <li>Enter/Verify your contact information and payment details</li>
  </ol>

